@TaskService_HostAddress = https://localhost:7150

### Create a task
POST {{TaskService_HostAddress}}/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Implement Task Service",
  "description": "Build REST API with CRUD operations",
  "status": "Todo",
  "originalEstimatedWork": 8
}

### List all tasks
GET {{TaskService_HostAddress}}/api/tasks

### Get task by id
@taskId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
GET {{TaskService_HostAddress}}/api/tasks/{{taskId}}

### Update task
PUT {{TaskService_HostAddress}}/api/tasks/{{taskId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Implement Task Service",
  "description": "Updated description",
  "status": "InProgress",
  "originalEstimatedWork": 10
}

### Delete task
DELETE {{TaskService_HostAddress}}/api/tasks/{{taskId}}
